metadataAttributes.Title: Introduction to SQL
metadataAttributes.Short Intro: Become an SQL power user!   By the end of this hands-on course, you’ll be able to complete complex tasks in SQL, including cleaning data and tuning the performance of your queries so they run quickly, even over giant data sets.
metadataAttributes.Skills: SQL Subqueries, SQL JOINs, SQL Window Functions, SQL Queries, SQL Aggregations, SQL Query Performance Tuning, Data Cleaning
